OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,7,FShehab Khan gives an update on how all
OL,8,Fof this might affect you
OL,10,FWords by Senior Business and Economics
OL,11,FProducer Jack Abbey
OL,13,FWe've had days of economic turmoil and
OL,14,Ffor the first time in a week,
OL,15,Ffinancial markets have finally seen
OL,16,Fsome gains - all because Donald Trump
OL,17,Fpaused some of his tariffs.
