OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FBoth the American S&P 500 and British
OL,7,FFTSE 100, good measures of how their
OL,8,Frespective markets are performing, are
OL,9,Fup by about 3% since yesterday's
OL,10,Fsuspension.
OL,12,FBut gains do not mean a full recovery.
OL,13,FThe American stock market had a tough
OL,14,Fday on Thursday and is down, and
OL,15,Fmarkets are still 8% behind where we
OL,16,Fwere when tariffs were first
OL,17,Fintroduced.
OL,19,FMarkets matter.
