OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FFor one, it impacts interest rates.
OL,7,FMarkets now expect them to be cut
OL,8,Ffaster to give the economy a boost and
OL,9,Fthat means mortgages coming down too.
OL,11,FWe're even starting to see some being
OL,12,Foffered at below 4% - Barclays today
OL,13,Fbecame the first major lender to do so.
OL,15,FOn top of that, a lot of people have
OL,16,Ftheir savings and pensions, at least
OL,17,Fin part, invested in stock markets and
OL,18,Facross the board pensions are down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
