OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FAJ Bell has crunched the numbers for
OL,7,FITV News and has calculated that in
OL,8,Fbroad terms, higher-risk pensions are
OL,9,Fdown 5.9%, medium risk 3.8% and low
OL,10,F1.9%.
OL,12,FExperts say don't panic though.
OL,14,FMost people will have their pensions
OL,15,Fmoved to safer assets in the years
OL,16,Fbefore retirement, and younger people
OL,17,Fhave time to ride out the volatility.
OL,18,FThose losses were also down on Monday
OL,19,Fwhen by comparison a higher-risk
OL,20,Fpension was down around 8%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
