OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FBut it wasn't stock market pain that
OL,7,Fcaused Trump to change his mind.
OL,8,FInstead - something else is likely to
OL,9,Fhave scared him.
OL,11,FRemember Liz Truss. Her political
OL,12,Fcareer was cut short when her economic
OL,13,Fpolicies spooked the markets and
OL,14,Fresulted in the cost of government
OL,15,Fborrowing going up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
