OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FSomething similar started happening in
OL,7,Fthe US in recent days. Spooked
OL,8,Finvestors started selling government
OL,9,Fbonds, which in turn acted to push up
OL,10,Finterest rates that the US government
OL,11,Fwould have to pay to borrow.
OL,13,FThere were serious concerns that this
OL,14,Fspike in the cost of borrowing would
OL,15,Fget out of control. That's why Trump
OL,16,Ffelt he had to act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
