OL,3,CHow the tariff turmoil is impacting UK
OL,4,Cmortgages and pensions
OL,6,FBut regardless we are not out of the
OL,7,Fwoods yet. Britain still faces tariffs
OL,8,Fof 25% on steel and aluminium and on
OL,9,Fcars, plus there's a base of 10% on
OL,10,Fall goods sold to the US.
OL,12,FSo while the big tariffs faced by the
OL,13,Frest of the world are on pause, the
OL,14,Ftrade war with China isn't and that
OL,15,Fhas the ability to set off market
OL,16,Fvolatility again.
